{"tid":583091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[思考人生]善良只係一種選擇","createTime":"2018-03-06T17:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T18:30:49.000Z","uid":171344,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f9e06a8465c065863e32b230675cc7aa04b3ce","tid":583091,"uid":171344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"人越大, 越覺得人生唔知為咩<br />\n唔知生存意義係為咩<br />\n做人要有目標聽得多, 但我從來搵唔到<br />\n只係更加明白世界既殘酷同無奈<br />\n<br />\n細個時個個都會教你相信別人<br />\n但大左就會知社會係教你提防別人<br />\n細個學識分享<br />\n但大個先知道自私先可以生存<br />\n自己好似只係戴住一個面具<br />\n最後&quot;善良&quot; 變成一個選擇<br />\n<br />\n努力係可以得到成果<br />\n但當你得到成果前<br />\n已經有一堆人用其他既手段得到成果<br />\n<br />\n呢排成日問自己, 生存其實為咩"},{"pid":"39050b4b44dd43fbbc2fb8131e945946b537e28d","tid":583091,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f5fecab0d5c7a6d2d37b4358a8ad78e9f371279","tid":583091,"uid":71712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 善良係一種態度"},{"pid":"b6b7658766e1b4913d468a78f25d457bf1e7f8fd","tid":583091,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"咁應該要點樣做人？"},{"pid":"bc1e25df74bfd817832b33a5e7381ee80d7d9fcd","tid":583091,"uid":171958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"ffe37cacd397d7bd26d9cce4efce6efb737ca37e","tid":583091,"uid":158741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"善良 係一種選擇，但自問 會唔會有時因為自己撩咗善良而高興先。"},{"pid":"691c427770e626a9bfe63a28bd626eb5e0744ac2","tid":583091,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"巴打有潛質讀 philosophy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab8922af12e644beb1179ca307d7a709c2edeb2","tid":583091,"uid":55390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"所謂善良其實到最後都係為左自我感覺良好<br />\n人就係自私 其實大家都係一樣"},{"pid":"27512376bb58cf66cb8b0928682d6b86881954a8","tid":583091,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"善良是邁向的第一步"},{"pid":"54424afb13e8908d21f9367f5f901e6fc4825a2b","tid":583091,"uid":154447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:07:32.000Z","msg":"依個社會 越善良既人越上唔到位<br />\n有錢有勢既人好多都自私諗自己<br />\n人類本應係有血有肉既生物 <br />\n會有惻隱之心<br />\n但隨住人大左 加上環境因素<br />\n有時瞞住良心都要做下衰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4563968a5e4c7e3a2653ab70bfbdeb12763313b6","tid":583091,"uid":50253,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"善者偽也<br />\n人之所以行善<br />\n係因為行善滿足到自己心靈<br />\n其實都係虛榮感既一種<br />\n但呢種已經係最高層次既善<br />\n<br />\n其次係想人地鍾意自己<br />\n亦係大多數善行背後既動機<br />\n常見於男歡女愛  朋友既關係入面<br />\n<br />\n可能聽完會反感<br />\n但人係動物   動物行為係需要有movitation<br />\n<br />\n如果要你做一個會眾叛親離 遺臭萬年既英雄<br />\n你會唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9be14df70793a7399a36034058e25d06d1fb597","tid":583091,"uid":171344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39050b4b44dd43fbbc2fb8131e945946b537e28d","tid":583091,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:10:45.000Z","msg":"都係20頭"},{"pid":"27dc54fca5a94b16b22230824e35d750dc6c38ab","tid":583091,"uid":171344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffe37cacd397d7bd26d9cce4efce6efb737ca37e","tid":583091,"uid":158741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"善良 係一種選擇，但自問 會唔會有時因為自己撩咗善良而高興先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"都會既, 但當自己善良被人利用<br />\n就真係好心酸下"},{"pid":"303e5ae28e73c2a72e3924eee165b58c5b24a4da","tid":583091,"uid":1713